longBusinessSummary: Wästbygg Gruppen AB (publ) operates as a construction and project development company in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, and Finland. It operates through three segments: Residential, Commercial, and Logistics and Industry. The company develops and constructs rental and tenant-owned apartments. It also builds and develops residential, commercial buildings, and community service properties; and logistics and industrial plants under the Logistic Contractor brand. Wästbygg Gruppen AB (publ) was founded in 1981 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden. Wästbygg Gruppen AB (publ) is a subsidiary of M2 Holding AB.
